#this is for running man game set
#yesterday game
#12people two-two cp
#assign four thievfs and one leader theivf  and the king
#for three rounds  each round can choose two cps and verficate the info of nums of theif
#game flow:
1.start-game :assigin each indetity for each person
2.one-round:game one :rule;crisma race:each cp can give a topic to race which is infident to win ,
win once can get points ,finaly  get most points  is winner ,and get rights to verify the identity
3.one-round end: each person get 30s to free chat theri ideas ,winners to execute the rights and
4.two-round:game two: rule:the fight on the bowl :all people divide into two groups
each group fight in the one bowl ,which cp can stay in bowl at last  is winner .
5.two-round end :rule sim to one round
6.three round: for last game ,the host will give a question,answer is which number ,corrcet numbers of people should be
hubbled ,each people can get one point ,finaly the get most points for people can get the win of game
7.three-round end :rule sim to one round
8.final :all people can vote for king and thievf leader ,guess for correct answer of king or leader is winner.
